author: lisa robinson
text: Oh, what a great day this has been!!  Boston can kick rocks... We are gonna be moving home.  If for no other reason, seeing my babies see their father in person for the first time in 4 years... There was so much JOY in their faces.. https://t.co/r2MVHIGUqT

author: lisa robinson
text: Man, I could have stayed home for this vacation.  All I've done is sleep, lol.  The hotel bed has seen me more than Columbia has.

author: lisa robinson
text: I'm telling y'all, God is trying to tell me something though.  I ran into my Lakeside Ave neighbor, and she told me that 3 houses just opened up across the street from her.  Including a 1 bedroom and a 3 bedroom.  I was REALLY tempted to go look at them. 😒

author: lisa robinson
text: Good Morning!  Happy Easter to those who celebrate.  About to bring the boys to see their dad for the first time in 4 years 😐.  Then off to dinner cooked by my daughter and the boys can open their baskets

author: lisa robinson
text: Gahh... My daughter took my suitcase with all of my clean clothes to her hotel & went out.  Welp.. these boys are gonna have to see Nana in her granny panties tonight, because I can't sleep in these clothes another night

author: lisa robinson
text: Gyatdamn.. I check into my hotel in Columbia just to hear about 10 people people being shot at the Columbian Mall.  I coulda stayed home for that isht.
